				aside.notes.
					If you are also unimpressed, please consider the Baryon Acoustic Oscillations, or consider visiting a big bang with an oxygenated helmet!

					So, there is a hidden language that speaks directly to our brain, forged through millennia of evolution, directly influenced by our interactions with the world and the sounds that have guided us. 

					This universal language can be used effectively to control moods and evoke emotions without any form of obvious communication.

					Music is a powerful tool. 

					So,
					to represent a human using technology it must...

