					//- During sleep your vital statistics are being controlled by your central autonomous nervous system, regulated by your unconscious brain. You don’t have to think to breathe or blink - this is the domain of the autonomous nervous system.

					By converting biometrics and emotions into data, it is possible to analyse and extract the user's intention and mood. 

